<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head lang="en">
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport"
          content="width=device-width, user-scalable=no, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, minimum-scale=1.0"/>
    <title></title>
    <style>
        .update {
	    display: none;
            position: fixed;
            z-index: 4;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            left: 0;
            top: 0;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
            font-family: "microsoft YaHei", sans-serif;
        }
        .update ul {
            list-style: none;
            position: relative;
            width: 300px;
            height: 300px;
            background: #ff8b00;
            color: #fff;
            left: 50%;
            top: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(-50%);
            border-radius: 14px;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 18px;
            animation: bling .7s infinite alternate;
        }
        .update ul li {
            line-height: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        .update ul li:first-of-type,
        .update ul li:last-of-type {
            padding-left: 0px;
        }
        .update ul li:first-of-type {
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .update ul button {
            height: 40px;
            background: #fff;
            border: 0;
            color: #dc7400;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            display: block;
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        @keyframes bling {
            to {
                box-shadow: 0 0 20px #ffad00;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="update">
    <ul>
        <li>更新提示：</li>
        <li>1.增加了下拉菜单的过渡效果！！！更加酷炫！！！</li>
        <li>2.修改了"去凑单"按钮的背景颜色，还增加了对应电商的图标！！！</li>
        <li><button>我知道了啊啊啊</button></li>
    </ul>

</div>
</body>
<script>
    //键的名字要改,不然大家读的都是一样的布尔值
    if(!localStorage.getItem("xxx1")){
        $(".update").show();
    }else{
        $(".update").hide();
    }
    $(".update button").YFLtap(function () {
        $(".update").hide();
        localStorage.setItem("xxx1","notNull");
    });
</script>
</html>